==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stated
<hw>Stat"ed</hw> <pr>(st⟦amac⟧t"⟦ecr⟧d)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Settled; established; fixed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He is capable of corruption who receives more than what is the
<qex>stated</qex> and unquestionable fee of his office.</q>
<rj><qau>Addison.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Recurring at regular times; not occasional; <as>as,
<ex>stated</ex> preaching; <ex>stated</ex> business
hours</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Statedly</ent>⟦br⟧
